headline: Royal Caribbean quietly makes ship decision customers demanded
summary: For years, Royal Caribbean executives have been asked the same question at nearly every public event, and they always give the same careful non-answer. They never told loyal customers they would not do what was being asked, but they also never said they would. When the company launched its newest ...
